# Kapruka AI Shopping Agent — Phase 1 Documentation
> Project Codename: **Kapruka Agent Challenge 2026**  
> Date: June 5, 2026  
> Author: Kapruka AI Team  

---

## 1. Overview

Phase 1 establishes the foundational architecture for the Kapruka AI Shopping Agent — a full-screen, conversational commerce experience built on top of the Kapruka MCP (Model Context Protocol). The goal is to create an immersive, Apple-inspired interface that feels native, premium, and delightful to use.

---

## 2. Tech Stack

| Layer          | Technology                          | Purpose                                       |
|----------------|-------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------|
| Framework      | Next.js (App Router)                | Full-stack React framework with SSR support   |
| Language       | TypeScript                          | Type safety across the entire codebase        |
| Styling        | Vanilla CSS (CSS Modules)           | Apple HIG-inspired design system              |
| AI SDK         | Vercel AI SDK (`ai`, `@ai-sdk/google`) | Streaming chat with tool-calling support     |
| MCP Client     | `@modelcontextprotocol/sdk`         | Connect to Kapruka's remote MCP endpoint      |
| Icons          | Lucide React                        | Clean, consistent iconography                 |
| Font           | Inter (via Google Fonts)            | Closest web equivalent to Apple's SF Pro      |

---

